&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Description:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a Junior Analytic Developer interested in working within a variety of environments to develop analytics based on data from multiple cyber sources. In this role, you will have a chance to work closely with mission stakeholders to create innovative applications and analytics and deploy solutions to customer-supported tools to automate and enable data and metadata analysis. The ideal candidate for this position will have experience in object-orientated languages like Java and Python and a desire to learn from highly respected senior developers. Please consider applying if you meet the following qualifications.&lt;/p&gt;
