&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;TS/SCI with polygraph security clearance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A Bachelor of Science (B.S.) degree in Computer Science or a related field and two (2) years of relevant experience is required. A Master of Science (M.S.) degree and zero (0) years, an Associate of Science (A.S.) degree and four (4) years, or a high school diploma/ GED and six (6) years of experience is also acceptable.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with object-oriented languages like Java and Python.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with PySpark.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with ETL processes and data integration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with JSON and BSON data formats.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with Pig, MapReduce, and Hadoop.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Desired Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of customer corporate tools and data repositories.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

