&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;TS/SCI with polygraph security clearance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A Bachelor of Science (B.S.) degree in Computer Science or a related field and eight (8) years of relevant experience is required. A Doctoral degree (PH.D.) and four (4) years, a Master of Science (M.S.) degree and six (6) years, or an Associate of Science (A.S.) degree and ten (10) years of experience is also acceptable.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
