&lt;li&gt;Network engineering experience with Arista, Cisco, and Juniper technologies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of Windows and Linux operating systems, application behavior, and network traffic analysis.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Desired Qualifications: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
