&lt;li&gt;Experience using learning management systems (LMS) or instructional development tools such as Moodle, Camtasia, Adobe Captivate, Articulate, or similar platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience conducting Windows host and network forensics.&lt;/li&gt;
